OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782388091
OL,3,CWoman jailed after driving over man
OL,4,Cthree times in fatal incident
OL,6,FA personal trainer who repeatedly
OL,7,Fdrove over a vulnerable man in the
OL,8,Froad has been jailed.
OL,10,FBolton Crown Court heard how Megan
OL,11,FMurphy, 26, drove over Darryl
OL,12,FTomlinson on an icy morning, while her
OL,13,Fvehicle's windows were heavily frozen,
OL,14,Fleaving her with severely restricted
OL,15,Fvisibility.
OL,17,FShortly before 6am on Thursday, 9
OL,18,FJanuary 2025, Murphy got into her car
OL,19,Fand reversed from an alleyway onto
OL,20,FPembroke Road in Wigan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
