OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782388091
OL,3,CWoman jailed after driving over man
OL,4,Cthree times in fatal incident
OL,6,FCCTV footage showed she positioned her
OL,7,Fvehicle facing against the direction
OL,8,Fof the one-way street before setting
OL,9,Foff.
OL,11,FThe footage also showed that her
OL,12,Fwindscreen and windows were visibly
OL,13,Ffrozen, significantly blocking her
OL,14,Fview.
OL,16,FAs Murphy drove forward, she failed to
OL,17,Fsee Mr Tomlinson, who had collapsed in
OL,18,Fthe road several hours earlier.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782388091
OL,3,CWoman jailed after driving over man
OL,4,Cthree times in fatal incident
OL,6,FTwo witnesses saw the vehicle
OL,7,Fapproaching him and desperately
OL,8,Fattempted to warn Murphy. One ran
OL,9,Ftowards the car shouting for her to
OL,10,Fstop and reverse, while another
OL,11,Frepeatedly sounded their horn.
OL,13,FAlthough Murphy brought her vehicle to
OL,14,Fa stop just inches from Mr Tomlinson,
OL,15,Fprosecutors said she was unable to see
OL,16,Fwhat the witnesses were pointing to
OL,17,Fbecause of the poor visibility through
OL,18,Fher frozen windows.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782388091
OL,3,CWoman jailed after driving over man
OL,4,Cthree times in fatal incident
OL,6,FShe then drove forward over Mr
OL,7,FTomlinson before reversing back over
OL,8,Fhim moments later. The court heard she
OL,9,Fthen moved forward again, causing the
OL,10,Ffront wheel of her vehicle to pass
OL,11,Fover him for a third time. Mr
OL,12,FTomlinson became trapped beneath the
OL,13,Fdriver's side of the car.
OL,15,FA witness called the North West
OL,16,FAmbulance Service, which alerted
OL,17,Fpolice to the incident.
OL,19,FDuring this time, Murphy phoned a
OL,20,Ffriend and told them: "I've ran him
OL,21,Fover but it's a smackhead."
OL,26,@|D@WOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782388091
OL,3,CWoman jailed after driving over man
OL,4,Cthree times in fatal incident
OL,6,FThe court heard Murphy also attempted
OL,7,Fto defrost her windows while Mr
OL,8,FTomlinson remained trapped beneath the
OL,9,Fvehicle, but was unsuccessful.
OL,11,FWhen officers arrived at the scene,
OL,12,Fthey used a witness's car jack to free
OL,13,FMr Tomlinson before beginning CPR.
OL,14,FParamedics arrived shortly afterwards,
OL,15,Fbut he was pronounced dead at around
OL,16,F6.21am.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782388091
OL,3,CWoman jailed after driving over man
OL,4,Cthree times in fatal incident
OL,6,FPolice noted Murphy's windscreen was
OL,7,Fstill visibly frozen when they
OL,8,Fattended. When questioned about why
OL,9,Fher vehicle was travelling the wrong
OL,10,Fway down the one-way street, she was
OL,11,Funable to provide an explanation.
OL,13,FInvestigators later discovered CCTV
OL,14,Ffootage showing Murphy had driven the
OL,15,Fwrong way along the same road on two
OL,16,Foccasions in the days leading up to
OL,17,Fthe collision.
OL,19,FMegan Murphy, from Ince, pleaded
OL,20,Fguilty to causing the death of a man
OL,21,Fby dangerous driving.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782388091
OL,3,CWoman jailed after driving over man
OL,4,Cthree times in fatal incident
OL,6,FShe was sentenced to six years in
OL,7,Fprison at Bolton Crown Court on
OL,8,FWednesday, 24 June.
OL,10,FDuring sentencing, members of Mr
OL,11,FTomlinson's family described the
OL,12,Fdevastating impact his death has had
OL,13,Fon their lives.
OL,15,FHis mother told the court that Darryl
OL,16,Fhad been born prematurely at just 26
OL,17,Fweeks weighing 2lb 4oz and had
OL,18,Fovercome countless challenges
OL,19,Fthroughout his life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782388091
OL,3,CWoman jailed after driving over man
OL,4,Cthree times in fatal incident
OL,6,FShe said: "I struggle to put into
OL,7,Fwords how I feel about losing my son,
OL,8,Fand all I can say is that I really
OL,9,Fdon't feel anything anymore since
OL,10,Flosing Darryl."
OL,12,FHis father described feeling as though
OL,13,Fhe had "died inside but was still
OL,14,Fbreathing" after learning of his son's
OL,15,Fdeath.
OL,17,FMr Tomlinson's brother said the family
OL,18,Fhad been further hurt by learning
OL,19,FMurphy had referred to Darryl as "a
OL,20,Fsmackhead" in a phone call to a friend
OL,21,Frather than calling for an ambulance.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@OO]uD@HOUvD@JO]{D@bOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782388091
OL,3,CWoman jailed after driving over man
OL,4,Cthree times in fatal incident
OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Carl Boydell, from Greater
OL,8,FManchester Police's Serious Collision
OL,9,FInvestigation Unit, said: "This was a
OL,10,Ftruly tragic and entirely avoidable
OL,11,Fincident that has resulted in the
OL,12,Fdevastating loss of a life.
OL,14,F"Our thoughts remain firmly with
OL,15,FDarryl's family and loved ones as they
OL,16,Fcontinue to come to terms with what
OL,17,Fhas happened.
OL,26,@qD@[OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782388091
OL,3,CWoman jailed after driving over man
OL,4,Cthree times in fatal incident
OL,6,F"This outcome reflects just how
OL,7,Fseriously the courts treat dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving. Motorists have a
OL,9,Fresponsibility to always follow the
OL,10,Frules of the road and to ensure their
OL,11,Fvehicle is safe before setting off.
OL,13,F"Even in cold weather, taking the time
OL,14,Fto properly clear windows and ensure
OL,15,Ffull visibility is essential. If you
OL,16,Fcannot see clearly, you cannot drive
OL,17,Fsafely."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
